{"title":"六月观麦（外一首）","authors":["高深"],"dates":[{"year":1994,"month":6,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"六月观麦（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高深"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦穗悄悄度过蜜月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又在构思粉白色的童话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同样的主题、色彩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同样的经历和命运"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁也不觉得千篇一律"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼唤太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也呼唤不大不小的南风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吐出尖锐的锋芒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成熟了也不低头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（不像稻谷作谦卑状）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成功在夏季长眠在夏季"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长眠而不逝灭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与齿轮手挽着手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拥抱天安门城楼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给一位村党支部书记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你从前流的汗水也是咸的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却没有给村民的生活"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"增添浓郁的滋味"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把一座大山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻成平地又堆成大山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有织出太多的绿叶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些日子已经过去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只留下沉积很深的记忆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和仍想抚摸的厚茧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今你和农民兄弟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都成为土地的知心人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以生命的一部分"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化作另一片绿色的生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你把汗水滴进泥土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你把心贴在垄台上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你把自信投入明天"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}